data.description: Welcome to this modern gem featuring 4 bedrooms, 2 bathrooms, and 1,735 square feet of meticulously redesigned living space. Built in 2019, this home has undergone a recent and comprehensive remodel, showcasing contemporary sophistication and functionality. The open-concept layout enhances the flow between the living, dining, and kitchen areas, creating an inviting atmosphere for both relaxation and social gatherings. The stylishly remodeled bathrooms and updated kitchen reflect the latest in design trends and offer a touch of luxury. With a perfect blend of recent construction and cutting-edge renovations, this residence provides a turnkey solution for those seeking a home that effortlessly combines modern living with timeless comfort.
